snippet.textDisplay: The only zoom worth bragging about is optical zoom. Anything else will result in loss. You might have some wiggle room taking a 12 megapixel photo with a 108 megapixel but you then lose the 9-pixels-into-1 trick!  So realistically the best they can do is maybe a 2x digital zoom combined with the 10x optical? They should have advertised this as 10x Optical zoom (actual cameras have been doing this for years) instead of some BS unusable 100x claim.
snippet.textOriginal: The only zoom worth bragging about is optical zoom. Anything else will result in loss. You might have some wiggle room taking a 12 megapixel photo with a 108 megapixel but you then lose the 9-pixels-into-1 trick!  So realistically the best they can do is maybe a 2x digital zoom combined with the 10x optical? They should have advertised this as 10x Optical zoom (actual cameras have been doing this for years) instead of some BS unusable 100x claim.
